45:48.946 --> 46:03.394 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: From clay pots
to entire
cities, a most unusual and
influential artist.

46:03.494 --> 46:05.830 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
