studio.

46:11.135 --> 46:16.374 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: When you make a
pot, the artist
Theaster Gates told me recently
in his studio,

46:16.474 --> 46:19.076 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
