how to shape
it.

46:19.176 --> 46:23.681 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THEASTER GATES: If it's clay,
then I have
to learn a lot about the
minerals that are

46:23.781 --> 46:29.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
