47:54.505 --> 47:59.577 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
them new life, like these
floorboards from
a community youth gymnasium that
was being

47:59.677 --> 48:00.978 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
