48:01.078 --> 48:03.180 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
THEASTER GATES: Instead of
demolishing it
and just kind of...

48:03.280 --> 48:05.049 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes, instead of
