48:22.833 --> 48:24.335 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
THEASTER GATES: Sure. Yes.

48:24.435 --> 48:27.772 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And not only
